---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <!-- HERO with upfront CTA via Beehiiv + promo -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h1 class="brand">Modern Compass</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Helping you find direction in the moments that matter most.
      </p>
      <p class="sublead">
        Modern Compass is a framework for accelerating growth in Self, Trust, Character, and Relationships.
      </p>

      <!-- Promo + Beehiiv embed as a single unit -->
      <div class="newsletter-embed">
        <img
          src="/Newsletter%20Promo.png"
          alt="Join 100+ subscribers and get this digital asset free"
          class="promo-img"
        />
        <script async src="https://subscribe-forms.beehiiv.com/embed.js"></script>
        <iframe
          src="https://subscribe-forms.beehiiv.com/261a3276-40ab-431a-8523-c85bec095b96"
          class="beehiiv-embed"
          data-test-id="beehiiv-embed"
          frameborder="0"
          scrolling="no"
          style="width: 595px; height: 225px; margin: 0; border-radius: 0; background-color: transparent; box-shadow: 0 0 #0000; max-width: 100%;"
          title="Subscribe to the Modern Compass newsletter"
        ></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT IS MODERN COMPASS -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2 class="h">What Is Modern Compass?</h2>
      <p>
        There are a lot of great self-improvement books, yet many skew academic or abstract. Modern Compass is different.
        It is built around four clear directions that are simple to remember and deep enough to guide real progress. It becomes your compass for tracking growth. Each direction has four layers that build on each other.
      </p>

      <img
        src="/Modern%20Compass%20Layers.png"
        alt="Modern Compass layers graphic"
        class="layers-img"
      />

      <p class="sublead centered">
        Each direction builds in layers. Start with the foundation, then move down as each layer builds on the previous one.
      </p>

      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="h3">Self</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Awareness</li>
            <li>Worth</li>
            <li>Confidence</li>
            <li>Control</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="h3">Trust</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Tenets of Trust</li>
            <li>Trust in Humanity</li>
            <li>Informed Trust</li>
            <li>Profound Trust</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="h3">Character</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Environmental</li>
            <li>Developed</li>
            <li>Authentic</li>
            <li>Transcending</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="h3">Relationships</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Empathy</li>
            <li>Resonance</li>
            <li>Affinity</li>
            <li>Loyalty</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

